reviewText: Do not buy this!  It is an exact copy of one of the dvd's that comes in the Eminem"The DVD Collector's Box.  They rewrapp the dvd and sell it as if it is another documentary.  Additionally, it is not authorized by Eminem.  It has Uncle Tom in it spewing untruths about Eminem.  There are no voices that represent Eminem.  There are some remarks by Eminmen all pulled from one interview.  Any true Eminem fan or person looking for the truth about the rapper should not buy this DVD!
